      {# Why We Built Ferni #}
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-display-sm text-ink mb-6">Why We Built Ferni</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-ink-muted space-y-4">
          <p>Our parents Doug and Betty Ford spent decades as therapists—sitting with people in their hardest moments. Our sister Mindy became a recreational therapist. We grew up surrounded by conversations about what it really means to help someone.</p>
          <p>But we also noticed something: <strong class="text-ink">some of the most important conversations in life happen at inconvenient times.</strong></p>
          <p>3am when you can't sleep because of work stress. During your commute when you need to process a big decision. Late at night when you just need someone to listen.</p>
          <p>Traditional support systems aren't designed for these moments. Therapy has waitlists and schedules. Friends have their own lives. And honestly? Sometimes you just want to think out loud without worrying about being a burden.</p>
          <p>We asked ourselves: <em>what if a lifetime of mental health wisdom could reach anyone, anywhere, anytime?</em></p>
          <p class="text-ferni font-semibold text-xl">That question became Ferni.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {# Our Approach #}
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-display-sm text-ink mb-6">Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-ink-muted space-y-4">
          <p>We didn't build another app. <strong class="text-ink">We built a relationship.</strong></p>
          <p>Six AI specialists, each with unique expertise, working together to support your growth. They hand off to each other naturally, bringing the right perspective at the right moment.</p>
          <p>And unlike other AI tools, Ferni is <strong class="text-ink">voice-first</strong>. Because the most meaningful conversations happen when you speak, not when you type. When you talk to Ferni, you're processing your thoughts in real-time—the same way you would with a trusted friend or coach.</p>
          <p>Most importantly: <strong class="text-ferni">Ferni remembers.</strong> Your goals. Your context. Your journey. Every conversation builds on the last.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {# What We Believe #}
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-display-sm text-ink mb-8">What We Believe</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-ink/5">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-ink mb-2">AI should be better than human.</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-muted">Perfect memory. Zero judgment. Constant presence. What human support can't offer.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-ink/5">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-ink mb-2">Growth happens gently.</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-muted">Small consistent actions beat heroic effort every time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-ink/5">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-ink mb-2">Privacy is non-negotiable.</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-muted">Your conversations are yours. We don't sell data. We don't train on your words. Period.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-ink/5">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-ink mb-2">Access matters.</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-muted">Life coaching shouldn't be a luxury. Everyone deserves support.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>

